properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Pt. St. George to Cape Mendocino CA out 10 nm; Coastal waters from Cape Mendocino to Pt. Arena CA out 10 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 29 at 2:43PM PST until January 30 at 9:00PM PST by NWS Eureka CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...NW swell building to 14 feet at 18 seconds, largest late
Thursday morning.

* WHERE...Pt St George to Cape Mendocino out 10 nm and Cape
Mendocino to Pt Arena out 10 nm.

* WHEN...From 3 AM to 9 PM PST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 3 AM TO 9 PM PST THURSDAY
